{"tid":2326561,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你見到人online exam出貓，你會唔會Report?","createTime":"2020-12-15T11:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T23:57:43.000Z","uid":376170,"like":5,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"286eb70035026fecd1c8895238141a15357a6d22","tid":2326561,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:41:50.000Z","msg":"借ac問<br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜五要開cam exam，講到明唔可以同人傾/online chat<br />\n<br />\n考完之後，會比30分鐘我地upload成份paper<br />\n<br />\nupload完之後其實就走得<br />\n<br />\n但係見有時間剩，就諗住睇吓同學嘅樣，話晒今個sem完全冇見過啲同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n走淨幾條友個陣，見到有一男一女個背景一模一樣，應該係屋企入面（係咪想笑人冇男/女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n之後仲要戴埋口罩，條仔個cam仲要影到條女啲頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果我report會唔會好多事？<br />\n<br />\n搞親人地又好似唔係太好咁，話哂人地辛苦咁多年時間都係為咗攞個degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者佢哋可能真係冇傾計？<br />\n<br />\n我又怕麻煩，所以都唔係好想report比professor"},{"pid":"2b09c1565ab7105a5ff5ca5758289909121b8aa5","tid":2326561,"uid":238919,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:42:18.000Z","msg":"report"},{"pid":"29b842ccd7a1e31735dfbbabeec10f82321f58d2","tid":2326561,"uid":370062,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"冇睇內容但睇標題會"},{"pid":"a9487d20fc455bf03f451b35dbe8415384c48c72","tid":2326561,"uid":139187,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"可以嘅，如果你肯定自己之後唔需要出貓既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ed8fad75efbac292eaa1ba1360cb51ee54def1","tid":2326561,"uid":308615,"like":9,"dislike":34,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"唔好多事"},{"pid":"32e3b7b6096c9633872aa9ae8ff9dbf1b6db2fc2","tid":2326561,"uid":139187,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"93ed8fad75efbac29